Game.....: Cannon Spike
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: November 16th, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

THE FUTURE NEEDS YOU!
Far into the future, a rogue group of terrorist robots wreak havoc on the world and its citizens. The World Peace Alliance formed the Anti-Robot Special Forces and it is their job to overthrow these radical robots. With an arsenal of weapons and high powered Motor Boots, you must lead a courageous legion of seven members through multiple levels of robotic terror, huge bosses and other evils. Strap on your Motor Boots and prepare yourself for the ultimate in speed, strategy and firepower. Its up to you to rid the world of the robot menace.

Game Features:
- High speed shooter pushes the limits of reflex and skill!
- Choose from seven characters, including Mega Man and Cammy!
- Non-stop action! Multiple levels of combat and awesome firepower.
